caption: Lovely, warm and touching little church. Full of life and secret spirituality.

A dynamic community, in constant search of the new life that Jesus Christ, the God-Man, brought into this world. Many Roman Catholics, Christians who, throughout history, have lost the authentic sense of Christian spirituality, can rediscover in this community the authentic taste of Eternal Life by sharing God through word, song, icons. and above all by the real and mysterious Body and Blood of the incarnate Christ, dead and resurrected for each of us and for all humanity, from one end of history to the other.

A place where heaven comes down to earth. I am glad that in my delegation in May I managed to participate in a liturgy in the morning. I am glad that liturgies are still held during the week. Thank God for everything!
Church located in the basement of the St Sulpice church. Welcomed all people. The services are partly in French, but there is always someone who can translate for you. Very active and united parish.
